msgid "Scenario III: Queen of Ash"
msgstr "冒险III：灰烬女王"

msgid ""
"Dr. Armitage thanks the waitress at Velma’s Diner as she sets two pieces of warm apple pie between you. The head librarian pushes one toward you with a strained smile. “Arkham is changing. The world is changing—for the worse, I fear—but at least we have pie.”\n"
"Together, you and Dr. Armitage piece together a disturbing picture of the situation at hand. “The Brethren of Ash are not conspirators,” Armitage says. “They are thralls, all of them. Thralls of an ancient goddess, one they call ‘Elokoss’.” Dr. Armitage shows you a grotesque woodcut of a gnarled tree with burning branches before continuing.\n"
"“After attending one of the cult’s secret gatherings, some prospective followers develop a strange bruise that marks them as one of Elokoss’s own. These followers are from all walks of life: rich and poor, weak and strong. Most importantly, these thralls have no idea that they are under her sway. Your mysterious pursuer is one such thrall. According to prophecy, the ‘Servant of Flame’ who attacked us at the university is the harbinger of the queen’s return. The servant gathers sacrifices to make way for their queen’s glorious rebirth. A rebirth they predict will happen this very evening.”"
msgstr ""
"维尔玛小餐馆的服务员放下两块热腾腾的苹果派，阿米蒂奇博士谢过了她。图书馆的负责人尽力挤出一个勉强的笑容：“阿卡姆在改变。世界都在变——恐怕，不是在变好——但至少我们还有苹果派。”\n"
"你和阿米蒂奇博士一起整理出眼前的局势，情况非常不妙。“灰烬同袍会不是阴谋的策划者。”阿米蒂奇说，“他们只是奴仆，全部都是。一位古代女神的奴仆，他们称其为‘俄洛寇斯’。”阿米蒂奇博士给你看了一幅古怪的木刻画，上面是一株扭曲的树，枝条全在燃烧。\n"
"“有些潜在的信徒，在参加教派的秘密集会之后，会长出奇怪的淤青，说明俄洛寇斯已将他们标为自己所有。这些信徒来自各行各业，不分贫富强弱。最重要的是，这些奴仆压根不知道自己已经在她的操控之下。你那个神秘的追兵就是一个这样的奴仆。根据预言，那个攻击大学的‘烈焰仆从’就是代表女王回归的使者。这些仆从为了女王的辉煌重生收集贡品。预言说重生就在今夜。”"

msgid "Because you are playing on Easy difficulty, add an [elder_thing] token to the chaos bag for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "因为你正在进行简单难度，在剧本之后的部分，在混乱袋中加入1个[elder_thing]标记。"

msgid "Because you are playing on Standard difficulty, add an [elder_thing] and a [tablet] token to the chaos bag for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "因为你正在进行普通难度，在剧本之后的部分，在混乱袋中加入1个[elder_thing]标记和1个[tablet]标记。"

msgid "Because you are playing on Hard difficulty, add an [elder_thing], [tablet], and a [skull] token to the chaos bag for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "因为你正在进行困难难度，在剧本之后的部分，在混乱袋中加入1个[elder_thing]标记、1个[tablet]标记和1个[skull]标记。"

msgid "Because you are playing on Expert difficulty, add an [elder_thing], [tablet], [cultist], and a [skull] token to the chaos bag for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "因为你正在进行专家难度，在剧本之后的部分，在混乱袋中加入1个[elder_thing]标记、1个[tablet]标记、1个[cultist]标记和1个[skull]标记。"

msgid ""
"The thought of your friend being sacrificed chills you to your core. Rather than piece together circumstantial evidence, you suggest that you search the Servant of Flame’s residence for some clue. Your search turns up several leads. An invitation to a secret meeting. A pair of scuffed muddy boots. A record of bootlegging operations in the Waterfront District. A photo of three faces lit by candlelight in the dark. Everything points to the Arkham sewers.\n"
"“A bit foolish, wouldn’t you think, for a cult that worships fire to conduct their business in the sewers?” Armitage chuckles. “But I believe you are correct.”\n"
"Together, you resolve to scour the sewers for any trace of your friend."
msgstr ""
"一想到你的朋友可能被当作祭品，你就感到毛骨悚然。你不想再拼凑琐碎的证据，建议直接去烈焰仆从的住处找找线索。结果还真让你找到了点东西：神秘集会的请柬、带泥的磨损靴子、滨水区的走私记录、一张照片，上面是黑暗中烛火照亮的三张人脸。所有一切都指向阿卡姆的下水道。\n"
"“一个崇拜火的教派，却把下水道当大本营，你不觉得有点蠢吗？”阿米蒂奇笑道，“但我相信你是对的。”\n"
"你们齐心协力，决定就算要把下水道翻个底朝天，也要找到朋友的下落。"

msgid ""
"The thought of your friend being sacrificed chills you to your core. Together, you and Dr. Armitage pore over the precious few clues you have gathered. After several hours of mind-numbing analysis, Armitage theorizes that the Brethren of Ash are conducting their ritual in the Arkham sewers.\n"
"“A bit foolish, wouldn’t you think, for a cult that worships fire to conduct their business in the sewers?” Armitage chuckles. “But it’s the only lead we’ve got.”\n"
"Together, you resolve to scour the sewers for any trace of your friend."
msgstr ""
"一想到你的朋友可能被当作祭品，你就感到毛骨悚然。你和阿米蒂奇博士一起，仔细研究收集到的寥寥几条线索。几个小时的绞尽脑汁后，阿米蒂奇分析说灰烬同袍会将在阿卡姆的下水道举行他们的仪式。\n"
"“一个崇拜火的教派，却把下水道当大本营，你不觉得有点蠢吗？”阿米蒂奇笑道，“但这是我们仅有的线索了。”\n"
"你们齐心协力，决定就算要把下水道翻个底朝天，也要找到朋友的下落。"

msgid "During setup, place 1 doom on the agenda."
msgstr "设置期间，在密谋上放置1个毁灭标记。"

msgid "Put Underground Cistern into play. <i>(See the diagram below for suggested location placement.)</i>"
msgstr "将【地下水库】放置入场。<i>（见下方的地点摆放位置建议）。</i>"

msgid "Shuffle each location in the <b>Sewers</b> encounter set so you do not know which is which and put each of them into play, unrevealed."
msgstr "混洗<b>下水道</b>遭遇组的所有地点，以使你无法分辨，将其全部放置入场，未揭示面朝上。"

msgid "Set Sluice Control aside, out of play."
msgstr "将【水闸控制台】放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play at Sewer Culvert."
msgstr "每位调查员从【下水道涵洞】开始游戏。"

msgid "<i>Note: During this scenario, remember that some locations have different location connection icons on their revealed sides!</i>"
msgstr "<i>注意：本场冒险期间，记住有些地点的已揭示面会有不同的地点连接图标！</i>"

msgid "Underground Cistern"
msgstr "地下水库"

msgid "Sewer Tunnels"
msgstr "下水道隧道"

msgid "Sewer Culvert"
msgstr "下水道涵洞"

msgid "You have a general sense of where the ritual is to take place. Each investigator begins the game with 1 clue <i>(from the token pool)</i>."
msgstr "你大概知道仪式会在哪里举行。每位调查员开始游戏带有1个线索<i>（从供应堆拿取）</i>。"

msgid "The Brethren of Ash have gotten wind of your violent tactics. Find each [[Cultist]] enemy in the <b>Ashen Pilgrims</b> and <b>Cultists</b> encounter sets, shuffle them together and put 1 [per_investigator] enemies from that set into play, each at a different Sewer Tunnels location."
msgstr "灰烬同袍会听闻了你的激进行为。找出<b>灰烬朝圣者</b>和<b>异教徒</b>遭遇组中每个[[异教徒]]敌人，将其混洗，从中将1[per_investigator]个敌人放置入场，每个位于不同的【下水道隧道】地点。"

msgid "Remove the Servant of Flame enemy from the game."
msgstr "将【烈焰仆从】敌人从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Set the Servant of Flame enemy aside, out of play."
msgstr "将【烈焰仆从】放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "If there are 3 or 4 players in the game:"
msgstr "如果游戏中有3位或4位玩家："

msgid "Gather the <b>Fire!</b> encounter set and set each copy of Fire! aside, out of play, along with both copies of the Collector reward asset and the Elokoss, Queen’s Knight, and Herald of Flame enemies."
msgstr "收齐<b>着火了！</b>遭遇组，将每张【着火了！】、每张【收藏家】奖励支援、【俄洛寇斯】敌人、【女王的骑士】敌人、【烈焰兆使】敌人放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "By defeating the Servant of Flame, you have brought them to their senses. As you take off their mask, they look up at you, confused."
msgstr "你击败了烈焰仆从，让这家伙回过神来。你摘下了面具，对方一脸困惑地看着你。"

msgid "Check your campaign log. Because David Renfield is the harbinger of Elokoss:"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。因为大卫·伦费尔德是俄洛寇斯的使者："

msgid "David snarls as you try to help him stand. “Leave me. I am a willing servant. I welcomed her into me. And now she will purge all in her cleansing flame,” he laughs weakly before drawing his last breath."
msgstr "你帮大卫站起来，他却冲你呲牙咧嘴：“别管我，我是自愿侍奉的。我欢迎她来我身上。现在她会用净化的火焰清除一切。”他虚弱地笑着，咽下了最后一口气。"

msgid "Each investigator may search their deck for a [[Tome]] or [[Spell]] card and play it, ignoring all costs."
msgstr "每位调查员可以查找其牌库，找出一张[[书籍]]或[[法术]]卡牌并打出，忽略所有费用。"

msgid "Check your campaign log. Because Cornelia Akely is the harbinger of Elokoss:"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。因为柯妮丽娅·阿克里是俄洛寇斯的使者："

msgid "Cornelia stares, bewildered, at her bloody hands. “I thought it was all a nightmare,” she says as you help her to her feet. She looks you over and her face furrows. “You’re hurt. I can help.”"
msgstr "柯妮丽娅一头雾水地瞪着自己血迹斑斑的双手：“我还以为这一切都是一场噩梦。”她在你的帮助下站了起来。她看看你，眉头皱了起来：“你受伤了，交给我吧。”"

msgid "Each investigator heals 3 damage."
msgstr "每位调查员治愈3点伤害。"

msgid "Check your campaign log. Because Naomi O’Bannion is the harbinger of Elokoss:"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。因为内奥米·欧巴尼恩是俄洛寇斯的使者："

msgid "“What kind of party is this?” Naomi bellows, then gives you a murderous look. “And who the hell are you?” You do your best to explain the situation as you help her to her feet."
msgstr "“这里在开什么派对？”内奥米吼着给了你一个凶狠的眼神，“你他妈的又是谁？”你一边扶她起来，一边尽力解释当下的情况。"

msgid "Each investigator gains 5 resources."
msgstr "每位调查员获得5资源。"

msgid "Check your campaign log. Because Sgt. Earl Munroe is the harbinger of Elokoss:"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。因为厄尔·门罗警司是俄洛寇斯的使者："

msgid "The officer’s face is frozen in a look of terror as you take off the mask. “Where am I?” he asks, almost childlike. “And what did I do?” he looks at his blood-spattered clothing in horror."
msgstr "你摘下警官的面具，他的表情立刻因为恐惧僵住了。“我在哪里？”他问的时候简直像个孩子。“我都干了什么？”他惊恐地望着自己血迹斑斑的衣服。"

msgid "Each investigator may search their deck for a [[Weapon]] asset and play it, ignoring all costs."
msgstr "每位调查员可以查找其牌库，找出一张[[武器]]支援并打出，"

msgid "Check your campaign log. Because Abigail Foreman is the harbinger of Elokoss:"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。因为阿比盖尔·福尔曼是俄洛寇斯的使者："

msgid "Abigail clasps your hands tightly as you pull off her mask. “Finish her. Elokoss must not awaken,” she coughs. The librarian hands you a crumpled note before passing out."
msgstr "你摘下阿比盖尔的面具，她紧紧地抓住了你的手。“消灭她。俄洛寇斯不能苏醒。”她咳嗽道。年轻的图书馆员交给你一张皱巴巴的笔记后就昏了过去。"

msgid "Each investigator may draw up to 3 cards."
msgstr "每位调查员可以抽取至多3张卡牌。"

msgid "Check your campaign log. Because Margaret Liu is the harbinger of Elokoss:"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。因为柳玛丽是俄洛寇斯的使者："

msgid "“This is just like that debacle at the Tick Tock Club,” Ms. Liu seethes as you help her to her feet. The singer is remarkably unfazed by the surrounding chaos. Rather than ask about the debacle, you point her in the direction of the exit."
msgstr "“这就像滴答俱乐部的那场灾难。”你把柳女士拉起来的时候，她正气着呢。这名歌手并未因周遭的混乱而有所动摇。你没问那场灾难是什么，而是向她指明了出口的方向。"

msgid "Each investigator heals 3 horror."
msgstr "每位调查员治愈3点恐惧。"

msgid "Each investigator earns 5 bonus experience for defeating Elokoss and for saving their friend."
msgstr "每位调查员取得5点奖励经验值，因其击败了俄洛寇斯，拯救了自己的朋友。"

msgid "Each investigator earns 5 bonus experience for stopping a blasphemous ritual."
msgstr "每位调查员取得5点奖励经验值，因其阻止了亵渎的仪式。"

msgid "Each investigator who did resign earns experience equal to the <b>Victory X</b> value of each card in the victory display."
msgstr "每位撤退的调查员取得经验值，数量等于胜利区所有卡牌的<b>胜利X</b>数值之和。"

msgid "Each investigator earns 3 bonus experience for escaping the deluge."
msgstr "每位调查员取得3点奖励经验值，因其逃出了洪水。"

msgid "Each investigator suffers 2 mental trauma and 2 physical trauma from their horrific experiences."
msgstr "每位调查员承受2点肉体创伤和2点精神创伤，因为其遭遇了恐怖的经历。"

msgid "Each investigator suffers 2 mental trauma and 2 physical trauma from the events of the evening."
msgstr "每位调查员承受2点肉体创伤和2点精神创伤，因为其经历了难忘的一晚。"

msgid "Each surviving investigator suffers 3 mental trauma, as they are wracked with guilt for leaving their friends behind."
msgstr "每位幸存调查员承受3点精神创伤，因为其无法摆脱抛弃朋友的罪恶感。"

msgid "Elokoss was reborn."
msgstr "俄洛寇斯重生。"

msgid "the investigators defeated Elokoss and the Brethren of Ash."
msgstr "调查员击败了俄洛寇斯和灰烬同袍会。"

msgid "the investigators stopped Elokoss’s glorious rebirth."
msgstr "调查员阻止了俄洛寇斯的辉煌重生。"

msgid "the investigators flooded the Brethren of Ash’s summoning ritual."
msgstr "调查员淹没了灰烬同袍会的召唤仪式。"

msgid "The investigators have earned the Collector campaign reward card. Add both copies of this card to the player card pool. <i>(see “Reward Cards” on page 23 of the rulebook)</i>."
msgstr "调查员取得【收藏家】剧本奖励卡牌。将本卡牌的所有同名卡牌加入玩家卡牌的收藏<i>（见规则手册23页的“奖励卡牌”）</i>。"

msgid "The investigators win the campaign, but it is only a matter of time until the followers of Elokoss rise again..."
msgstr "调查员剧本胜利，但俄洛寇斯的追随者卷土重来只是时间问题……"

msgid "Each investigator who did not resign is <b>killed</b>."
msgstr "每位未撤退的调查员<b>阵亡</b>。"

msgid "Dr. Armitage barely escapes the sewers alive, wracked with guilt at leaving his companions behind. By dawn, an unquenchable fire has spread through all of Easttown, claiming countless lives. Although the Arkham Fire Department tries its best, the flames rage for three days before finally dying out. Those who fled whisper of unspeakable visions – a terrifying, ghoulish faces staring out of the flames – that still haunt them. Doctors and nurses are still unable to identify the source of the victims’ strange bruises, which will not heal. Any trace of Armitage’s companions, as well as the Brethren of Ash, has been eradicated in the inferno."
msgstr "阿米蒂奇博士仅以身免，逃出了下水道。抛弃同伴的罪恶感一直萦绕着他。到了早展，无可抑制的火焰席卷了东城区，夺走了数不清的性命。尽管阿卡姆消防局竭尽全力，大火还是烧了整整三天。侥幸逃脱的人还会嘟囔着不可名状的幻象—火焰中有一张骇人的病态面孔凝视着—这在他们的心中挥之不去。医生和护士也无法辨认受害者身上奇怪且无法治愈的淤青究竟从何而来。阿米蒂奇博士的同伴，还有灰烬同袍会，他们的踪迹都在炼狱中烧得一干二净。"

msgid ""
"Against all odds, the vessel of the ancient evil Elokoss has been destroyed, and the cult’s plans to bring her to this plane foiled. Dr. Armitage tends to the cultists as they reawaken. You find your friend among them, frightened and confused, but otherwise unharmed. As you explain the awful events of the evening, they listen intently. While escorting them and the rest of the innocents out of the sewers, you notice a strange, familiar mark on their neck. The bruise has lightened, and is only faintly visible, but it is still there.\n"
"It may only be a matter of time until the mark reawakens, and more followers of the Queen of Ash rise again to resurrect their goddess. You vow you will be ready, should that day come again."
msgstr ""
"你排除万难，摧毁了远古邪魔俄洛寇斯的容器，化解了教派想让她复生的密谋。阿米蒂奇博士前去照料醒来的异教徒。你发现你的朋友也在其中，惊慌失措，但毫发无损。你向朋友解释昨晚的可怕遭遇，对方听得专心致志。你护送朋友和其余的无辜者从下水道里出去，发现他们脖子上有奇怪但熟悉的印记。淤青已经淡了，几不可见，但确实还在。\n"
"也许假以时日，印记还会重现，会有更多灰烬女王的信徒再次想让女神重生。你发誓你会做好准备，迎接那天的到来。"

msgid ""
"A howling wind pelts you with cinders. Dr. Armitage pulls a battered tome out of the hands of a fallen cultist and chants a guttural, inhuman language. A loud crack, as of splitting timber, resounds through the cistern, and the flaming tree turns to powdery ash before your very eyes. All around you, the cultists drop their weapons and stop in their tracks, looking suddenly lost. They are no longer under Elokoss’s sway.\n"
"You find your friend among them, frightened and confused, but otherwise unharmed. All trace of the mark on their neck has vanished, and the rest of the cult seem to have returned to normal, with no memory of the events of the evening. Still, your experience tonight leaves you fearful. In the months ahead, the slightest hint of smoke sets your pulse racing. The flames have subsided, but you can’t shake the nagging feeling that somewhere deep below the city, the embers of Elokoss’s rage continue to smolder."
msgstr ""
"呼啸的风把灰烬刮到了你身上。阿米蒂奇博士从倒下的异教徒手里夺过一本破旧的典籍，从喉咙里发声念出非人的语言。巨大的喀啦声在水库中回响，仿佛是木柴劈裂。燃烧的树木在你眼前化作齑粉。你周围的异教徒全都扔下了武器，停下了脚步，茫然若失。他们再也不受俄洛寇斯的控制了。\n"
"你发现你的朋友也在其中，惊慌失措，但毫发无损。他们脖子上的印记都消失不见，教派剩下的人看来也恢复了正常，只是不记得这一晚都发生了什么。不过，今晚的经历还是让你心惊肉跳。接下来的几个月里，哪怕是一点点烟也让你心跳加速。烈焰已经平息，但你还是心神不宁，或许城市底下深处，俄洛寇斯怒火的余烬还在阴燃。"

msgid "The old sluice gate screeches open, loosing a deluge of fetid sewage. Down the corridors, you hear the torrent of water accompanied by the screams of countless cultists. Rather than try to run, you accept your fate. It is clear that there is no escape. You did what had to be done. As the muck rises rapidly to your ankles, then your knees, then your neck, you think of your friend and Dr. Armitage, and the countless others who have likely drowned. You sacrificed yourself and them to stop the return of an ancient evil. You only hope your sacrifice was not in vain."
msgstr "老旧的水闸吱嘎作响，放出恶臭的污流。廊道深处，你听到激流声中夹杂着数不清的异教徒尖叫。你没有试图逃跑，接受了自己的命运。显然你也无路可逃。你做了应该做的。污泥迅速漫上你的脚踝、膝盖、脖子，你想到了你的朋友和阿米蒂奇博士，以及这里数不清的其他人，他们多半也会淹死。你牺牲了自己，牺牲了他们，阻止了远古邪魔的回归。你只希望你的牺牲没有白费。"
